  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "On Fenris, Ragnar of the Thunderfist tribe is left dying after Strybjorn Grimskull destroys his family and his world. The Space Wolves take both enemies to the Fang, where gene-seed trials, Blood Claw brutality and Wolf Priest Ranek's discipline turn tribal fury into Chapter loyalty. Ragnar's hatred of Strybjorn has to survive pack-bond, war and the Curse of the Wulfen, especially when his friend Kjel falls to the beast within. A harsh coming-of-age saga of ice, blood-feud and the making of Ragnar Blackmane.",
